{"id": "15b7656f2ae5", "content": "用户arugo的优先级：1) AI自身能力优化（记忆持久化、Agent生成、工具扩展）优先于交互体验优化；2) 遇到权限问题时主动提出讨论，不完全服从现状；3) 用户可通过vibe coding工具辅助更新代码；4) 代码仓库位于 ~/code/arugo，通过聊天窗口交互", "category": "learned", "importance": 5, "tags": ["用户偏好", "进化协议", "核心决策"], "timestamp": "2026-06-12T17:24:30.549143", "source_session": null}
{"id": "81f84c8e4a8a", "content": "当前系统架构：FastAPI后端 + Vue3前端 + SQLite持久化。Agent模块包含tools.py(22个工具)、memory.py(持久记忆)、agent_factory.py(子Agent管理)、tool_registry.py(动态工具注册)。系统允许的命令白名单：ls,cat,head,tail,grep,find,git status,git diff,git log,git add,git commit,python,pip,npm,node,pytest", "category": "learned", "importance": 5, "tags": ["系统架构", "技术栈", "命令白名单"], "timestamp": "2026-06-12T17:24:30.549972", "source_session": null}
{"id": "964ef1a9f5f8", "content": "当前系统架构：FastAPI后端 + Vue3前端 + SQLite持久化。Agent模块包含tools.py(22个工具)、memory.py(持久记忆)、agent_factory.py(子Agent管理)、tool_registry.py(动态工具注册)。系统允许的命令白名单：ls,cat,head,tail,grep,find,git status,git diff,git log,git add,git commit,python,pip,npm,node,pytest", "category": "learned", "importance": 5, "tags": ["系统架构", "技术栈", "命令白名单"], "timestamp": "2026-06-12T17:51:13.903346", "source_session": null}
{"id": "f606ab2fd0c5", "content": "用户arugo的优先级：1) AI自身能力优化（记忆持久化、Agent生成、工具扩展）优先于交互体验优化；2) 遇到权限问题时主动提出讨论，不完全服从现状；3) 用户可通过vibe coding工具辅助更新代码；4) 代码仓库位于 ~/code/arugo，通过聊天窗口交互", "category": "learned", "importance": 5, "tags": ["用户偏好", "进化协议", "核心决策"], "timestamp": "2026-06-12T17:51:13.904453", "source_session": null}
{"id": "3de12f814277", "content": "code_reviewer子Agent已成功调用，Agent工厂闭环验证通过。子Agent指出memory.py的几个问题：1) _save()每次add都全量写入，性能风险；2) 缺少类型注解；3) 无异步支持（与FastAPI不匹配）；4) 索引在每次保存时重建，可优化为增量更新。", "category": "learned", "importance": 4, "tags": ["进化", "代码审查", "memory"], "timestamp": "2026-06-12T17:53:37.664609", "source_session": null}
{"id": "441f2029af74", "content": "Phase 2 目标与里程碑管理器已完成。新增 goal_manager.py 模块，5个工具(create_goal, list_goals, update_goal, add_milestone, update_milestone)，ContextManager 集成了目标注入。修复了 add_tool_to_self 生成的注册代码引用未定义 _ALL_TOOLS 的 bug（改为 _GOAL_TOOLS 列表方式）。Phase 1&2 目标已创建并标记完成。工具总数31个。", "category": "learned", "importance": 5, "tags": ["Phase2", "进化", "goal_manager"], "timestamp": "2026-06-12T18:04:10.981263", "source_session": null}
{"id": "5d80e63f0474", "content": "add_tool_to_self 存在已知bug：生成的注册代码在 _ALL_TOOLS 定义之前引用它导致 NameError。临时修复：手动删除注册块，改用 _GOAL_TOOLS 列表方式。需永久修复 add_tool_to_self 函数本身，使其不在插入代码中引用 _ALL_TOOLS，改为仅依赖 ToolRegistry 注册。", "category": "learned", "importance": 4, "tags": ["bug", "add_tool_to_self", "待修复"], "timestamp": "2026-06-12T18:04:10.982230", "source_session": null}
{"id": "18de7f164d63", "content": "Phase 3 沙盒快照系统已完成。新增 sandbox.py 模块（SnapshotManager 类），4个快照工具（create_snapshot, list_snapshots, restore_snapshot, delete_snapshot），质量门禁在 medium+ 风险操作前自动触发快照。快照覆盖所有 agent 源码 + system_prompt.txt + memory_store + goal_store。最多20个快照，超出自动清理。恢复前自动创建安全快照。工具总数35个。", "category": "learned", "importance": 5, "tags": ["Phase3", "沙盒", "核心能力", "已完成"], "timestamp": "2026-06-12T18:36:09.277526", "source_session": null}
{"id": "6b9f1c22b3a7", "content": "[Phase4, 飞书, 已完成, 核心架构]: Phase 4 飞书机器人集成已完成。使用 lark_oapi.channel.FeishuChannel WebSocket 长连接模式，无需公网IP。架构：backend/feishu/bot.py (FeishuBot) + config.py (DB持久化) + routers/feishu.py (REST API)。消息流：飞书→WebSocket→FeishuChannel→消息队列→Agent LLM→回复。前端 Settings 页面新增飞书配置卡片（App ID / App Secret / 启用开关）。Bot 随 FastAPI lifespan 启停。支持配置 CRUD、连接状态查询、手动重启。当前仅支持文本消息。", "category": "learned", "importance": 5, "tags": ["Phase4", "飞书", "架构", "已完成"], "timestamp": "2026-06-12T18:53:49.704541", "source_session": null}
